original_title: The Spanish Stallion: Shalina Devine's True Power of Sex
overview: Ambitious filmmaker Rocco Siffredi presents the climactic eighth chapter of his epic adult serial based in the world of boxing. "The Spanish Stallion: Shalina Devine's True Power Of Sex" concludes the saga with six scenes of sweaty, very physical action, some of it in the ring.
